love_song

library(jiebaR)
library(stringr)

# Get txt file paths
fps_m <- list.files('male', full.names = T)
fps_f <- list.files('female', full.names = T)

# Initialize jiebaR
seg <- worker()

# determining song names
name_m <- vector('character', length(fps_m))

for (i in seq_along(fps_m)) {
  name_m[i] <- basename(fps_m[i])
}

name_f <- vector('character', length(fps_f))

for (i in seq_along(fps_f)) {
  name_f[i] <- basename(fps_f[i])
}

# determining lyrics
lyric_m <- vector('character', length(fps_m))

for (i in seq_along(fps_m)) {
  l_m <- try(readLines(fps_m[i], encoding = 'UTF-8')) 
  if ('try-error' %in% class(l_m)) {break} 
  else readLines(fps_m[i], encoding = 'UTF-8') %>% str_squish()
  segged_m <- segment(l_m, seg)
  lyric_m[i] <- paste0(segged_m, collapse = ' ')
}
## Error in file(con, "r") : 
lyric_f <- vector('character', length(fps_f))

for (i in seq_along(fps_f)) {
  l_f <- try(readLines(fps_f[i], encoding = 'UTF-8')) 
  if ('try-error' %in% class(l_f)) {break} 
  else readLines(fps_f[i], encoding = 'UTF-8') %>% str_squish()
  segged_f <- segment(l_f, seg)
  lyric_f[i] <- paste0(segged_f, collapse = ' ')
}
## Error in file(con, "r") : 
# Combine results into dfs
male_df <- tibble::tibble( = seq_along(fps_m),  = '',  = name_m,  = lyric_m)
female_df <- tibble::tibble( = seq_along(fps_f),  = '',  = name_f,  = lyric_f)
library(tidytext)
library(dplyr)
library(readxl)

stopwords <- read_excel('ch_stop_words.xlsx')

tidy_male <- male_df %>%
  unnest_tokens(output = '', input = '', token = 'regex', pattern = ' ') %>%
  anti_join(get_stopwords(), by = c('' = 'word')) %>%
  anti_join(stopwords, by = c('' = ''))
  
freq_male <- tidy_male %>% 
  group_by() %>% 
  summarize( = n()) %>%
  arrange(desc()) %>%
  print()

library(quanteda)
library(stm)
library(ggplot2)

tidy_both <- rbind(male_df, female_df) %>%
  unnest_tokens(output = '', input = '', token = 'regex', pattern = ' ') %>%
  anti_join(get_stopwords(), by = c('' = 'word')) %>%
  anti_join(stopwords, by = c('' = ''))

dfm_both <- tidy_both %>% 
  count(, , sort = TRUE) %>%
  cast_dfm(, , n)

dfm_male <- tidy_male %>% 
  count(, , sort = TRUE) %>%
  cast_dfm(, , n)

dfm_female <- tidy_female %>% 
  count(, , sort = TRUE) %>%
  cast_dfm(, , n)

topic_model_both <- stm(dfm_both, K = 4, verbose = FALSE, init.type = "Spectral")
topic_model_male <- stm(dfm_male, K = 2, verbose = FALSE, init.type = "Spectral")
topic_model_female <- stm(dfm_female, K = 2, verbose = FALSE, init.type = "Spectral")

td_beta_both <- tidy(topic_model_both)

td_beta_both %>%
    group_by(topic) %>%
    top_n(5, beta) %>%
    ungroup() %>%
    mutate(topic = paste0(' ', topic),
           term = reorder_within(term, beta, topic)) %>%
    ggplot(aes(term, beta, fill = as.factor(topic))) +
    geom_col(alpha = 0.8, show.legend = FALSE) +
    facet_wrap(~ topic, scales = "free_y") +
    coord_flip() +
    scale_x_reordered() +
    labs(x = NULL, y = expression(beta), title = '')

td_beta_male <- tidy(topic_model_male)

td_beta_male %>%
    group_by(topic) %>%
    top_n(5, beta) %>%
    ungroup() %>%
    mutate(topic = paste0(' ', topic),
           term = reorder_within(term, beta, topic)) %>%
